  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The bond with your Wildfire Spirit can save you from death. If the spirit is within 120 feet of you when you are reduced to 0 Hit Points and thereby fall &amp;Reference[Unconscious apply=false], you can cause the spirit to drop to 0 hit points. You then regain half your Hit Points and immediately rise to your feet.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a Long Rest.</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-xlY8s6zAFMZD1MEI\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Brink of Death Heal</strong> activity will heal you to half your max HP, but the dropping of the wildfire spirit to 0 HP is not automated.</p></section>",
